goonhilly
---------
A simple api service for receiving log messages.

To implement advanced user-agent logging:

1) visit https://github.com/tobie/ua-parser
2) clone the ua-parser module into the same folder as goonhilly (or into the site_packages folder of your Python library)
3) change the hyphen in the module name to an underscore (ln -s ua-parser ua_parser)
4) create an __init__.py file in the module folder (touch ua_parser/__init__.py)
5) Change the UA_PARSER setting in settings.py to True